---
title: One-Pan Chicken Stir-Fry Tacos with Tangy Slaw, Green Pepper, Sriracha Mayo & Crispy Onions
description: We’re always up for a sweet and savory dinner pairing, and these tacos are just that. Chicken breast strips are cooked in a sweet soy glaze until sticky and tender. They’re stuffed into steamy tortillas, along with a tangy, cilantro-flecked cabbage slaw. Of course, we’d never skip out on taco toppings, and these don’t disappoint: There’s creamy, spicy sriracha mayo and crispy fried onions. It’s all ready in just 15 minutes—life is sweet (and savory), friends.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pan-chicken-stir-fry-tacos-c2cf20eb.jpg
